A media personality has just died on a car crash in Joburg this morning, Joburg Metro Police spokesman, Wayne Minaar has confirmed. Minaar said there was an accident between Grayston Drive and Malboro Drive on the M1 North. According to Minaar, the car just went off the freeway and the person died. "There was a business card on this person and he was linked to a Public Relations company. That is all that I can say at the moment because I'm not sure if the next of kin have been informed yet. The person was driving in Mercedes Benz," said Minaar.